snippet.title: Oliver learns good habits with Diana and Roma
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma teach Oliver good habits - using the potty, brushing his teeth, cleanliness and safety at home, and good manners when visiting.

00:00  Diana and Roma help Oliver Potty Train
03:39 Diana and Roma show Oliver Why brushing teeth is essential

12:36 Diana Teaches Oliver Etiquette and Good Manners
17:40 Fun Cleaning with Parents
24:27 Diana and Roma Show Little Oliver How to Behave
